    <body>
      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="S1201951">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-S1201951-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-S1201951-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-S1201951-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">July 6, 1736.&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-S1201951-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-S1201951-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-S1201951-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">We have not had two hundred drops of rain these six weeks past.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-S1201951-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-S1201951-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-S1201951-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1">I know you love <hi rend="italics">Alexandrines</hi>; for which reason I closed the above madrigal with one. I think it is of a very good proportion, which I hope you will set to musick; and pray let me have a base, and second treble, with what other decorations and graces, you can better design than I can direct.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-S1201951-line-1" n="1">Our river is dry,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-S1201951-line-2" n="2">And fiery the sky;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-S1201951-line-3" n="3">I fret and I fry</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-S1201951-line-4" n="4">Just ready to die:</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-S1201951-line-5" n="5">Oh, where shall I fly</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-S1201951-line-6" n="6">From <hi rend="italics">Ph≈ìbus</hi>'s eye?</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-S1201951-line-7" n="7">In bed, when I lye,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-S1201951-line-8" n="8">I soak like a pye;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-S1201951-line-9" n="9">And I sweat, oh, I sweat, like a hog in a stye.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
